00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:48.289
Act or something, some supporters of the bill
probably wouldn't vote for it. If a bill wins

00:01:48.289 --> 00:01:51.329
the majority of the votes in the Senate, it
moves onto the House. Thanks Thought Bubble.

