00:06:04.710 --> 00:06:08.010
The founders set up these structural hurdles
of the bicameral Congress and the presidential

00:06:08.010 --> 00:06:12.310
role in legislation to reduce the likelihood
that authoritarian laws would pass. Congress

00:06:12.310 --> 00:06:16.060
added procedural hurdles like committees and
filibusters for the same reason. You can argue

00:06:16.060 --> 00:06:19.590
that Congress has become dysfunctional, but
looking at the process of lawmaking, it's

00:06:19.590 --> 00:06:21.860
hard to argue that this isn't by design.

